<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<section class="guide-hero-v35">
  <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
  <h1>A focused exchange for used wall printer machines.</h1>
  <p>Wall Printer Exchange helps sellers present used wall printers clearly and helps buyers discover machines worth reviewing. We are an introduction platform, not a marketplace that holds funds or guarantees machine condition.</p>
</section>

<section class="guide-grid-v35">
  <article>
    <span>Platform role</span>
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>We collect seller submissions, organize machine information, publish approved listings, and help serious buyers request seller contact or submit buying requirements.</p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>Transaction boundary</span>
    <h2>What we do not do</h2>
    <p>We do not inspect machines, provide escrow, process payments, arrange shipping, handle customs, provide installation, or issue warranties for used machines.</p>
  </article>
  <article>
    <span>Best fit</span>
    <h2>Who it is for</h2>
    <p>The site is built for commercial buyers, dealers, print-service businesses, and sellers who need a clearer channel for used wall printer opportunities.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<section class="guide-note-v35">
  <h2>Simple operating principle</h2>
  <p>We make machine discovery and introductions easier. Buyers and sellers still verify every technical, financial, legal, and logistics detail directly before any deal.</p>
</section>
